ind":"italic_en","text":"curtain, hung down; hung down loosely; was pendent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pendulous:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner the verb is said of a garment, or a portion thereof, and of hair, or a lock of hair, &c.]. (Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstrxY fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"استرخى فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 6."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstrxY fiY raA^oyihi baEoda","text_ar":"استرخى فِى رَاْيِهِ بَعْدَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quw~apK","text_ar":"قُوَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, weak in his opinion after being strong"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAar, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xrE","text_ar":"خرع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstrxY bihi AlA^amoru","text_ar":"استرخى بِهِ الاَمْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, T, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astrxt HaAluhu","text_ar":"استرخت حَالُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astrxt bihi HaAluhu","text_ar":"استرخت بِهِ حَالُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, became good with him after straitness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK;) or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became in a good state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in ample, unstraitened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plentiful, circumstances,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in explanation of the first of these phrases,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after straitness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA.) A poet says, (S,) namely, Tufeyl El-Ghanawee, (TA,)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"faA^ab~ala waA@sotaroxaY bihi AlxaTobu baEodamaA\n                      \n                     \n                        A^asaAfa walawolaA saEoyunaA lamo yuw^ab~ili"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And he acquired camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"numerous camels, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, became good"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after his cattle had perished; and had it not been for our labour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exertion, he would not have acquired camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"numerous camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, TA:) or the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstrxY bh AlxTb","text_ar":"استرخى به الخطب"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroxaAhu xaTobuhu","text_ar":"اَرْخَاهُ خَطْبُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[explained above: see 4]. (T, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","T","TA","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}